      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَنْ دَخَلَ اَلْكَعْبَةَ بِسَكِينَةٍ وَ هُوَ أَنْ يَدْخُلَهَا غَيْرَ مُتَكَبِّرٍ وَ لاَ مُتَجَبِّرٍ غُفِرَ لَهُ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2150 - Imam (as) said: \"Whoever enters the Kaaba with tranquility, meaning they enter it without arrogance or oppression, will have their sins forgiven.\""
        ]
      }
